README Environmental Data

Data in this folder are from many sources. Attempts have been made to gather data from as close to Appledore as possible

For full details on source and how annual means were calculated see 'env_data_source.xlsx' file

Quick links to data sources:
SST https://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oisst/optimum-interpolation-sea-surface-temperature-oisst-v20
AirT https://www.ndbc.noaa.gov/station_page.php?station=iosn3
Waves (tba)
Snow https://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/cdo-web/datasets/GHCND/stations/GHCND:USC00273626/detail
Precipation https://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/cdo-web/datasets/GHCND/stations/GHCND:USC00273626/detail
Chlorophyll https://neo.sci.gsfc.nasa.gov/view.php?datasetId=MY1DMM_CHLORA&year=2019
Global pH https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/indicators/ocean-acidification-3/assessment
NAO https://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/precip/CWlink/pna/nao.shtml


R Library for Heatwave Analysis:
http://search.r-project.org/library/heatwaveR/html/block_average.html


